[Version 1.3.0  2018-10-13  Philipp Leibfried]
 * JavaDoc is complete for all classes, interfaces and annotations
 * Project structure and test cases improved; run 'unattended' on command line
 * Various tweaks, removed some unnecessary code

[Version 1.2.0  2018-09-20  Philipp Leibfried]
 * Added @CorbaClientInterceptor annotation and corresponding bean postprocessing code
 * Added @CorbaServerInterceptor annotation and corresponding bean postprocessing code
 * Added @CorbaServiceContextManager annotation and corresponding bean postprocessing code
 * Added support for service context management and standalone interceptors
 * PoaBean injects itself into servant locators and activators if those implement PoaInjectable
 * Convenience methods for creating object references added to PoaBean class
 * Much better, more meaningful integration tests 

[Version 1.1.0  2018-09-14  Philipp Leibfried]
 * Added @CorbaDefaultServant annotation and corresponding bean post processing code
 * Changed name of NamingContext bean class to NamingContextBean to prevent confusion
 * Enhanced PoaBean to provide access to the POACurrent, inject POA into DefaultServant
 * Added tests for DefaultServant and the @CorbaDefaultServant annotation 

[Version 1.0.0  2018-09-10  Philipp Leibfried]
 * Added @CorbaServant annotation and corresponding bean post processing code
 * Added @CorbaRef annotation and corresponding bean post processing code
 * Added @ServantLocator and @ServantActivator annotations and corresponding bean post processing code

[Version 0.0.1  2013-12-31  Philipp Leibfried]
 * First iteration
 * All beans fully functional
 